<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shan-AI — פרופיל אישי</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Heebo:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* ── Shared DSS design tokens ── */
        :root {
            --bg-deep:   #070b12;
            --bg-card:   #0f1826;
            --border:    #1a2d47;
            --border-hi: #1e3a5f;
            --cyan:      #00d4ff;
            --cyan-dim:  rgba(0,212,255,0.09);
            --purple:    #8b9cf4;
            --green:     #10b981;
            --red:       #ef4444;
            --text-1:    #e2e8f0;
            --text-2:    #64748b;
            --text-3:    #344156;
            --mono:      'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            --ui:        'Heebo', sans-serif;
        }

        @keyframes blink { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0.3} }

        /* ── Navbar ── */
        .navbar {
            background: rgba(7,11,18,0.96) !important;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
            height: 50px;
            position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
        .navbar::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, var(--cyan) 30%, var(--purple) 70%, transparent 100%);
            opacity: 0.2;
        }
        .navbar-brand {
            font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1.02rem; font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--cyan) !important; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; text-decoration: none;
        }
        .brand-pulse {
            width: 5px; height: 5px; background: var(--cyan); border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--cyan); animation: blink 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .nav-link {
            font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-2) !important;
            padding: 0.22rem 0.6rem !important; border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.14s; white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .nav-link:hover { color: var(--text-1) !important; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
        .nav-link.nav-active { color: var(--cyan) !important; background: var(--cyan-dim); }
        .nav-pending-dot {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            width: 16px; height: 16px; background: var(--red); color: #fff;
            font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.55rem; border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 3px; box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(239,68,68,0.5);
            animation: blink 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .user-chip {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
            padding: 3px 10px; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-2);
        }
        .user-online { width: 5px; height: 5px; background: var(--green); border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--green); }
        .logout-btn {
            font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-3) !important;
            text-decoration: none; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 4px; transition: all 0.14s; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }
        .logout-btn:hover { color: var(--red) !important; background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1); }

        body { background: #0f1117; color: #e0e0e0; font-family: var(--ui); }
        .navbar { background: #1a1d2e !important; border-bottom: 1px solid #2d3047; }
        .card { background: #1a1d2e; border: 1px solid #2d3047; border-radius: 12px; }
        .form-control, .form-select {
            background: #0f1117; border: 1px solid #2d3047;
            color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 500;
        }
        .form-control:focus, .form-select:focus {
            background: #0f1117; color: #ffffff;
            border-color: #8b9cf4; box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(139,156,244,0.25);
        }
        .form-control::placeholder {
            color: #7a7a7a;
            opacity: 1;
        }
        .form-select option { background: #1a1d2e; color: #ffffff; }
        .form-label { color: #d0d8f0; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .section-title { color: #8b9cf4; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;
            border-right: 3px solid #8b9cf4; padding-right: 10px; }
        .info-badge { background: #2d3047; border-radius: 8px; padding: 6px 14px;
            color: #8b9cf4; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-dark d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between position-relative">
    <a href="/dashboard/" class="navbar-brand text-decoration-none"><div class="brand-pulse"></div>SHAN-AI / DSS</a>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-1 flex-wrap">
        <a href="/dashboard/" class="nav-link">📊 דשבורד</a>
        <a href="/dashboard/decisions" class="nav-link">📋 החלטות</a>
        <a href="/dashboard/users"    class="nav-link">👥 משתמשים</a>
        <a href="/dashboard/files"    class="nav-link">📁 קבצים</a>
        <a href="/dashboard/ask"      class="nav-link">💬 שאל</a>
        <a href="/dashboard/learning" class="nav-link">🎓 למידה</a>
        <a href="/dashboard/logs"     class="nav-link">📊 לוגים</a>
        <a href="/dashboard/projects" class="nav-link">📂 פרויקטים</a>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
        <div class="user-chip"><div class="user-online"></div>{{ current_user.username }}</div>
        <a href="/logout" class="logout-btn">🚪 יציאה</a>
    </div>
</nav>


<div class="container py-5" style="max-width: 600px;">

    {% if msg %}
    <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show">
        ✅ {{ msg }}
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if error %}
    <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show">
        ❌ {{ error }}
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="card p-4">
        <div class="section-title mb-4">👤 הפרופיל שלי</div>

        <!-- Read-only info -->
        <div class="mb-4 p-3" style="background:#0f1117; border-radius:8px;">
            <div class="row g-2">
                <div class="col-6">
                    <div class="text-muted small">שם משתמש</div>
                    <div class="fw-semibold">{{ user.username }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <div class="text-muted small">תפקיד במערכת</div>
                    <div class="fw-semibold">{{ role_labels.get(user.role.value, user.role.value) if user.role else "—" }}</div>
                </div>
                {% if user.email %}
                <div class="col-12">
                    <div class="text-muted small">אימייל</div>
                    <div>{{ user.email }}</div>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="col-6">
                    <div class="text-muted small">טלגרם</div>
                    <div>{% if user.telegram_id %}<span style="color:#28a745;">✅ מחובר</span>{% else %}<span class="text-muted">לא מחובר</span>{% endif %}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Editable fields -->
        <form method="POST" action="/profile/{{ token }}">
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">שם תפקיד <span class="text-muted small">(ניתן לעריכה)</span></label>
                <input type="text" name="job_title" class="form-control"
                       value="{{ user.job_title or '' }}"
                       placeholder="לדוגמה: מנהל מגזר פיקוח">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">🎯 תחומי אחריות <span class="badge bg-info text-dark" style="font-size:0.65rem;">משמש ל-RACI AI</span></label>
                <textarea name="responsibilities" class="form-control" rows="3"
                          placeholder="לדוגמה: מכרזים ורכש, חוזי קבלנים, ניהול ספקים&#10;פירוט תחומי האחריות המרכזיים שלך — ה-AI ישתמש בזה לשיוך RACI חכם">{{ user.responsibilities or '' }}</textarea>
                <small class="text-muted">💡 ככל שהתיאור מדויק יותר, שיוך ה-RACI יהיה חכם יותר</small>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label class="form-label">מקום בהיררכיה <span class="text-muted small">(מספר — 1 = הכי גבוה)</span></label>
                <input type="number" name="hierarchy_level" class="form-control" min="1"
                       value="{{ user.hierarchy_level or '' }}"
                       placeholder="לדוגמה: 3">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-4">
                <label class="form-label">מנהל ישיר</label>
                <select name="manager_id" class="form-select">
                    <option value="">— ללא מנהל —</option>
                    {% for u in all_users %}
                    <option value="{{ u.id }}" {% if user.manager_id == u.id %}selected{% endif %}>
                        {{ u.username }}{% if u.job_title %} — {{ u.job_title }}{% endif %}
                    </option>
                    {% endfor %}
                </select>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100">💾 שמור שינויים</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
